cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.CE 

The paper proposes a method for learning causal models from observational and interventional data, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method is applied to reconstruct a cellular signaling network, which falls under the category of systems biology (cs.SI, cs.SY). The paper also introduces a novel way of modeling interventions, which could be relevant to the field of control engineering (cs.CE).
